text: Cherry Hill Road is a common road name in English-speaking places, including: *Cherry Hill Road (Calverton–College Park, Maryland) *Cherry Hill Road (Baltimore) *Cherry Hill Road (Reisterstown, Maryland) *Cherry Hill Road (Philippi, West Virginia) *Cherry Hill Road (Parsippany, New Jersey), exit 42 off Interstate 80 ==See also== *Cherry Hill (disambiguation)
title: Cherry Hill Road
